reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Light weight high storage lab top
reviews.reviewText: This laptop came installed with window 11. It has such a great speed. I was able to run multiple high consumption programs simultaneously with out any lag. I was able to run a high CPU intensive game with no problem at all. The storage is superb with the RAM at 24GB and with 1024 NVMe SSD. I also like the fact that is very light weight. As a business traveller myself, this lab top came in handy. It fits well on the small tables on planes, and also very light to carry around. The price was a little high for being a not usual brand of laptop. But, I am very satisfied about the Performance, features and style of this laptop. It has a modern look and shape. Based on my experience so far, I would recommend this laptop for all those cpu lovers.
